{"tid":1020659,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/Steam] Arma 3多人軍事沙盒週未免費試玩 + Steam 66% off","createTime":"2019-02-13T17:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T12:29:05.000Z","uid":164307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf4bc06744b7ad8745e338bf2d5412965658885","tid":1020659,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/o4g_tF7EOk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo4g_tF7EOk4&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyETmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=9731b88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o4g_tF7EOk4</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">ARMA 3 <br />\n武裝衝突3</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n由Bohemia Interactive所製作既《ARMA》系列之一，係2013年9月12日上架既軍事模擬沙盒遊戲。Bohemia工作另外一隻較為人所熟悉既製作係DayZ，其實亦係由Arma遊戲模式演變出黎。而PUBG更加係玩家PlayerUnkown喺Arma 3當中所整既自製模組，最後將其製成遊戲。但就算係咁，香港多人識PUBG同DayZ都多過元祖Arma3。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzHYqv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzHYqv5.jpg&h=3db42744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">常見問題</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁其實Arma3玩咩架呢?</span> <br />\nBohemia Interactive原本係一間為現實軍隊設計軍事訓練模擬既公司，唔信可以查下VBS2。咁佢哋亦將系統簡化成為老少咸宜既《ARMA》系列。遊戲主要取決於玩家既喜好去決定。數數遊戲模式都成十幾種，除咗官方既Campaign，PVP之外，亦有Exile(Arma 3 DayZ)，King of The Hill，Altis Life，Wasteland等等數之不盡既模式。再加上唔同玩家整既模組，呢隻game既潛力實在唔可以輕視。就算話己經出咗5年有多，但製作團隊亦經常推出新內容，例如話上個月出既Warlord。跨<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有人可能問點解唔玩Squad, Post Scriptum呢?</span><br />\n試問呢兩隻game係咪可以做到唔係打完一場就收皮既回合制先? Arma 3既優點就係玩家自由度大。或許Squad呢類遊戲畫質上略勝一籌，但唔好唔記得Arma3係13年產物，而且一場地圖大小可以係佢哋既四五倍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢睇落控制好似好複雜咁喎...</span><br />\n其實黎黎去去咪又係WASD，滑鼠左鍵開槍右鍵瞄，最多比多個zxcv既爬踎跨掣同i掣背包。除非你加mod啦，唔係既話都啲正路野。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77KsiRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77KsiRn.jpg&h=73a96214&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">招募</span></div></strong><br />\n睇完咁多廢話之後，假如你對軍事模擬有興趣又想揾香港軍事模擬隊伍既話，可以㩒入下面個post。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/988234\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/988234</a><br />\nBrotherhood of Wolf [BOWHK]，狼群，係一隊廣東話既Arma3軍事模擬隊伍。團隊作風係以輕鬆半擬真既態度打機。背景以德國聯邦國防軍為藍本，我哋有時都會打下唔同國家唔同時期。我哋自己擁有獨立既伺服器，每逢星期六日準時九點鐘開波打自製既Arma3 Coop Mission。<br />\n<br />\nWebsite: <a href=\"https://brotherhoodofwolf.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbrotherhoodofwolf.com%2F&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyETmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=bc11832b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://brotherhoodofwolf.com/</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/BOWHK2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FBOWHK2018&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyETmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=c0430898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/BOWHK2018</a><br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/BAPZxXW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FBAPZxXW&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyETmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=c5ab3d95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/BAPZxXW</a>"},{"pid":"4a05140383d62b4d7e6170e6aab153a93e4ade46","tid":1020659,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3836dbef8e1d932a8078e8900cb661050574c1e","tid":1020659,"uid":164307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T12:29:05.00